Scholars Publishing, pp. 57&ndash;80</li>

<li>Knuuttila, Simo, 1993, &ldquo;Trinitarian Sophisms in Robert
Holcot&rsquo;s Theology,&rdquo; in Stephen Read (ed.), <em>Sophisms in
Medieval Logic and Grammar</em>, Dordrecht, Boston, London: Kluwer
Academic Publishers, pp. 348&ndash;56.</li>

<li>Libera, Alain de, 1991a, &ldquo;Roger Bacon et la
r&eacute;f&eacute;rence vide: sur quelques ant&eacute;c&eacute;dents
