Paris: J. Vrin, pp. 85&ndash;120.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1991b, <em>C&eacute;sar et le
Ph&eacute;nix. Distinctiones et Sophismata Parisiens du XIIIe
Si&egrave;cle</em>, Pisa: Scuola Normale Superiore.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2002, &ldquo;R&eacute;f&eacute;rence et
modalit&eacute; selon l&rsquo;Anonymus Erfordiensis Q 328
(pseudo-Robert Kilwardby)&rdquo;, <em>Archives d&rsquo;Histoire
