Leiden-Boston-K&ouml;ln: Brill, pp. 49&ndash;64.</li>

<li>Reina, Elena Maria, 2002, <em>Hoc hic et nunc, Buridano, Marsilo
di Inghen e la conoscenza del singolare</em>, Firenze: Leo S.
Olschki.</li>

<li>Rijk, L. M. de, 1967, <em>Logica modernorum</em>, Volume II,
Assen: Van Gorcum.</li>

<li>Robertson, David G., 2002, &ldquo;A patristic theory of proper
names&rdquo;, <em>Archiv f&uuml;r Geschichte der Philosophie</em>, 84:
1&ndash;19.</li>

<li>Rosier-Catach, Ir&egrave;ne, 1983, <em>La grammaire
sp&eacute;culative des modistes</em>, Lille: Presses Universitaires de
Lille.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 1990, &ldquo;Signes et sacraments: Thomas
d&rsquo;Aquin et la grammaire sp&eacute;culative,&rdquo; <em>Revue des
sciences philosophiques et th&eacute;ologiques</em>, 74:
392&ndash;36.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2004, <em>La Parole Efficace. Signe,
rituel, Sacr&eacute;</em>, Paris: Seuil.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2008, &ldquo;Le Glosule super Priscianum:
s&eacute;mantique et universaux&rdquo;, <em>Documenti e studi sulla
